    dc:description "FIGURES 51–65. Montistrongylus ignati n. gen., n. sp. 51. male, transverse section, anterior body; 52. female, transverse section, anterior body; 53. male, anterior end lateral view; 54. male, transverse section, mid body; 55. female, transverse section, mid body; 56. male, transverse section, posterior body; 57. female, transverse section, posterior body; 58. male, anterior end showing beginnings of synlophe ridges; 59. genital cone, ventral view; 60. genital cone, lateral view; 61. gubernaculum, lateral view; 62. spicules, distal tips; 63. dorsal ray; 64. female, posterior end, lateral view; 65. bursa, flattened out. Scales are in m." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5301331/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

